06:07.790 --> 06:15.130
we could change it to the center, like this and we can also change the size of the title,

06:15.270 --> 06:17.950
maybe like this.

06:17.990 --> 06:19.000
Now this looks good,

06:19.070 --> 06:23.450
so let's close that menu and what else can I show you?

06:23.570 --> 06:28.090
Well maybe the background, at the moment we don't have any background.

06:28.250 --> 06:31.880
If we turn that on, you don't see a difference,

06:32.060 --> 06:33.460
let's see why this is not visible.

06:33.620 --> 06:36.930
So we click right here, scroll down a little bit,

06:37.310 --> 06:42.560
well you can see that we have the color set to white and this is why we cannot see any background right

06:42.560 --> 06:43.220
now.

06:43.640 --> 06:49.340
