06:49.340 --> 06:51.300
around with the transparency.

06:51.650 --> 06:57.170
To be honest, I don't want to have a background color in our report so we can turn it off right here

06:57.620 --> 06:59.180
and close that.

06:59.390 --> 07:06.700
Now the last thing I want to show you is that border option down here. If we turn that on, you can see

07:06.800 --> 07:13.010
if we unselect that visualization quickly that we now have that little border around our visualization

07:13.270 --> 07:21.630
and if we click that again, go to the formatting menu, scroll down, open that menu, then we can define the color

07:21.630 --> 07:22.650
of that border,

07:22.860 --> 07:26.410
so we will keep it black because I think this looks good.

07:26.760 --> 07:28.810
